1 AN ACT concerning
2 Montgomery County Planning Board and Washington Suburban Sanitary
3 Commission – Open Meetings – Live Streaming Requirement
4 MC/PG 101–25
5 FOR the purpose of altering the requirement that the Montgomery County Planning Board
6 and the Washington Suburban Sanitary Commission, respectively, stream live video
7 or audio of their open meetings to apply only to meetings held at certain locations;
8 and generally relating to open meetings of the Montgomery County Planning Board
9 and the Washington Suburban Sanitary Commission.
